	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Firstly, a big anouncement by Mr. Inafune: two brand new Mega Man games. The much awaited Mega Man Legends 3 had been announced, after several years of wait. Next, a developer room... with feedback from fans... and all that stuff we loved so much... for nothing.
<br />
<br />A prototype had been promised to be playable... but then, it was "delayed for improvement". Yes... of course. Now, the game is no more. I'm sad.
<br />
<br />What about you?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
